Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:24.51,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我為了不讓其毀壞而太過於珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:30.43,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也輸入郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:36.30,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又將其刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:38.70,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這樣的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:41.87,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將其打破的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:45.71,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}為我帶來契機的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:49.69,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心將其緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:53.27,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將現在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:56.76,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}雖然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:02:00.63,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使將碎片全部收集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:03.83,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必須用自己的雙手將其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:06.53,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}極其珍視的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:09.88,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕將其失去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:15.57,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但是我所希望的這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.85,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}都存在於此
